### ============================================
### 1. CREAR ÓRDENES
### ============================================

### 1.1 Crear orden PRESENCIAL (En restaurante)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "PRESENTIAL",
  "waiterId": {{waiterId}},
  "tableNumber": "Mesa 5",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "5b377969-a21b-4bd5-a5fd-28736c5bf3bb",
      "productType": "DISH",
      "quantity": 1,
      "notes": "Sin cebolla, extra picante"
    }
  ]
}

### 1.2 Crear orden ONLINE (Domicilio/Takeout)
POST {{host}}
//Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "ONLINE",
  "customerId": {{customerId}},
  "tableNumber": null,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "dish_id_example_2",
      "productType": "DISH",
      "notes": "Bien caliente"
    },
    {
      "productId": "addition_id_example_2",
      "productType": "ADDITION",
      "notes": null
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================
### 2. CONSULTAR ÓRDENES
### ============================================

### 2.1 Obtener todas las órdenes (con paginación)
GET {{host}}/{{page}}/page
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 2.2 Obtener detalle de una orden específica
GET {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### 3. ACTUALIZAR ÓRDENES
### ============================================

### 3.1 Cambiar estado a IN_PROGRESS
PUT {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### 3.2 Cambiar a COMPLETED
PUT {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### 3.3 Cambiar a DELIVERED
PUT {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}

### ============================================
### 4. CANCELAR Y ELIMINAR ÓRDENES
### ============================================

### 4.1 Cancelar una orden
PATCH {{host}}/{{orderId}}/cancel
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4.2 Eliminar una orden
DELETE {{host}}/{{orderId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### ============================================
### FLUJO COMPLETO: ORDEN -> PAGO CON STRIPE
### ============================================
### 1️⃣  Crear orden (usar 1.1 o 1.2)
### 2️⃣  Copiar orderId de la respuesta
### 3️⃣  Ir a Payment.http
### 4️⃣  Usar orderId para crear pago con Stripe
### 5️⃣  Validar que el pago aparece con status CONFIRMED
